project_descr: Enhancement of Investment Climate for Employment Generation

outputs.output_descr: In line with the framework of the 2013-2016 United Nations Development Assistance Framework (UNDAF) and the UNDP  Country Programme Action Plan for 2013-2016, UNDP will support the implementation of key development priorities in the Sudan National Strategic Development Plan of 2012-2016. Within this context, UNDP will support interventions related to development of private sector and youth employment.  In this regard, this Project Initiation Plan (PIP) will support the efforts of Government of Sudan to increase employment opportunities for youth  through developing a conducive investment clima
